Package com.ibm.team.repository.client.util

Provides secondary client-side-only APIs for the Repository component.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IClientLibraryContext Provides special access to the team repository from the client libraries for accessing service interfaces.
IClientLibraryContext.IServiceRunnable The IServiceRunnable interface should be implemented by any class whose instances are intended to be executed as a long-running cancelable operation that makes calls to service methods.
IEvent A description of an event originating from some event source.
IEventSource Represent a generic event source.
IListener Generic event handler interface.
IPropertyChangeEvent A description of a property change that has occurred for some object and originated from some event source.
ThreadPool.Task The signature of tasks accepted by the ThreadPool.
